# Sudoku Cloudflare Worker (Single JS File)

This project is now a **single JavaScript Cloudflare Worker**:

- `worker.js` (contains Worker handler + embedded HTML/CSS/JS game)

## Features
- Sudoku puzzle generation with unique-solution checks
- Three difficulties: easy, medium, hard
- Timer, mistakes limit, hint, check, reset, and solve
- Touch-first controls optimized for iPad
  - Safe-area support (`env(safe-area-inset-*)`)
  - Large tap targets for buttons and grid cells
  - Improved mobile web app meta settings

## Run locally with Wrangler
```bash
npx wrangler dev worker.js
```

Then open the local URL shown by Wrangler.

## Deploy
```bash
npx wrangler deploy worker.js
```
